	<section xml:id="adv-branching-summary">
		<title>Summary</title>
		<p>Today, we learned about:</p>
		<ul>
			<li> Syntax of the <c>switch()</c> statement</li>
		  	<li>
		  		<p>You can nest loops inside loops. Just make sure to:
		  			<ul>
		  				<li>Use a new loop counter for each loop</li>
		      			<li>Remember your curly braces</li>
		    		</ul>
		    	</p>
		    </li>
		  	<li>You can nest if statements inside loops or loops inside if statements.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</chapter>